<div class="sec">How It Works</div>
<div class="fcard">
  <div class="fcard-d">
    PIN switching lets cashiers hand off the register without logging out. The new cashier enters their 4-digit PIN — no email or password needed. The system auto-clocks out the previous cashier and clocks in the new one. All subsequent transactions are attributed to the new cashier until another switch happens.<br><br>
    <strong style="color:var(--amber)">Security:</strong> The cart is preserved during switches but can optionally be cleared. Manager override (PIN from MANAGER or OWNER role) is required for voids, refunds, and discount overrides.
  </div>
</div>

