<div class="sec">What Syncs in Real-Time</div>
<div class="fcard">
  <div class="fcard-d">
    <strong style="color:var(--green)">Instant sync:</strong> Inventory counts (when a sale depletes stock, ALL registers see the updated count), customer loyalty points, product price changes, active promotions/discounts<br><br>
